references.title: k-Space weighted image contrast (KWIC) for contrast manipulation in projection reconstruction MRI
Dynamic MRI with projection reconstruction and KWIC processing for simultaneous high spatial and temporal resolution
Linearization improves the repeatability of quantitative dynamic contrast-enhanced MRI.
